  "name": "Belt of Regeneration",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This belt is crafted from rubbery troll hide that's green and orange in color. You gain 15 temporary Hit Points the first time you invest the belt in a day. When you invest the belt, you either increase your Constitution score by 2 or increase it to 18, whichever would give you a higher score.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You tighten the belt one notch to gain a regeneration effect. For [[/r 2d4]] rounds, at the start of your turn each round, you recover [[/r 15[healing]]]{15 Hit Points} unless you took acid or fire damage since the start of your previous turn.</p>"
